<item>
            <title>[SEC-2537] net.sourceforge.nekohtml dependency missing for openid</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-2537</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;spring-security-openid has a dependency on openid4java which declares a provided dependency for net.sourceforge.nekohtml &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;spring-security-opened should provide this dependency by pulling it explicitly in pom.xml by adding &lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;dependency&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;net.sourceforge.nekohtml&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;nekohtml&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;version&amp;gt;1.9.20&amp;lt;/version&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;scope&amp;gt;compile&amp;lt;/scope&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/dependency&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
